and stay as we are?

03:47.480 --> 03:48.799
Cos I miss you.

03:51.640 --> 03:53.278
Think about it.

04:05.560 --> 04:07.152
Got nothing to say to me?

04:07.240 --> 04:09.470
I was wondering where to start.

04:11.320 --> 04:13.038
It's been tough...

04:13.120 --> 04:15.509
doing what I had to do, but I did it.

04:15.600 --> 04:16.952
What do you want, a medal?

04:17.040 --> 04:19.474
- I want a bit of respect.
- What for?

04:19.560 --> 04:24.190
Filling your veins with shite
or fucking some scrubber behind my back?

04:24.280 --> 04:29.593
They'll be no more drugs. And should
you continue to distance yourself,

04:29.680 --> 04:32.558
I'll take that as my cue
to find my comforts elsewhere.

04:32.640 --> 04:35.359
You're in no position to make any
demands after what you've done.

04:35.440 --> 04:38.193
And you're in no position to tell me
how I can and can't live my life.

04:38.280 --> 04:41.397
- So where do we go from here?
- That's very much up to you.

04:41.480 --> 04:46.110
If you are going to be my wife,
stand by my side, that's fine.

04:46.200 --> 04:48.430
But if you think
you can rip my balls off

04:48.520 --> 04:51.273
and tell me what I can and can't do,
that isn't.

04:52.640 --> 04:53.834
Your call.

05:06.040 --> 05:08.031
Colin...

05:08.120 --> 05:10.076
If you're nervous, don't be.

05:10.160 --> 05:13.232
Whatever you requested,
we've heard it a thousand times before.

05:13.320 --> 05:15.311
- Eh, Kelly?
- Heard it, done it.

05:15.400 --> 05:17.914
So what is it,
a bit of slap and tickle? M and S?

05:18.000 --> 05:20.389
- Domination?
- Cross-dressing?

05:20.480 --> 05:22.755
Not you breast feeding,
then shit in a nappy, is it?

05:22.840 --> 05:24.637
Does it involve a glass table
and a number two?

05:26.560 --> 05:28.516
It's ball...

05:28.600 --> 05:30.238
room.

05:31.560 --> 05:34.074
Is that like teabagging?

05:39.400 --> 05:40.799
UNZIPPING

05:48.360 --> 05:49.952
Fred and Ginger.

05:50.040 --> 05:52.315
So what? Shoes on, wig on?

05:52.400 --> 05:54.391
DVD on while we do the dirty?

05:57.840 --> 06:00.195
It's a bit more complicated
than that.

06:03.200 --> 06:06.397
Things'll change. I'll try.

06:06.480 --> 06:09.552
At least say you'll think about it.

06:09.640 --> 06:11.551
OK.

06:14.960 --> 06:16.313
Reckon she'll come round?

06:16.400 --> 06:18.914
She's as stubborn as I am,
so she's gonna make me suffer.

06:19.000 --> 06:20.319
But, yeah, she'll come round.

06:20.400 --> 06:23.358
Go get your glad rags on,
you've got a party to get to.

06:23.440 --> 06:25.670
- I can't leave you on your own.
- Early night for me.

06:25.760 --> 06:28.593
- Bath and bed. I'll lock up.
- You don't mind?

06:28.680 --> 06:30.830
I'll be glad to see the back of you.
Go on.

06:34.720 --> 06:36.631
PHONE RINGS

06:40.120 --> 06:41.269
Hello?

06:42.680 --> 06:44.113
Hello?

06:51.280 --> 06:53.191
Right, that's downstairs finished.

06:53.280 --> 06:55.032
- Bathroom next.
- It's done.

06:55.120 --> 06:57.156
- The skirtings'll need cleaning.
- Done.

06:57.240 --> 07:00.118
- Bedrooms.
- Done. I did say.

07:00.200 --> 07:01.394
But I'll just check.

07:01.480 --> 07:04.916
Look, you wanted me to do more,
I've done it, and you're still not happy.

07:05.000 --> 07:07.355
I just want to help.

07:07.440 --> 07:10.352
All the time, right,
I lumbered you with all this,

07:10.440 --> 07:13.716
it was wrong, and I apologise, right?

07:13.800 --> 07:17.076
But I know now,
it's my responsibility, not yours.

07:20.240 --> 07:23.437
- Right, so what do you want me to do?
- Eh? I don't know.

07:23.520 --> 07:25.078
Form a cult, squeeze your spots,

07:25.160 --> 07:27.276
do whatever teenagers
are supposed to do.

07:44.360 --> 07:45.554
Yvonne, it's me!

07:49.720 --> 07:51.995
- What the fuck is all this about?
- I needed to see you.

07:52.080 --> 07:53.229
You can't. You're dead.

07:53.320 --> 07:56.153
You have no idea what it's
been like for me since I left.

07:56.240 --> 07:59.755
And I've had it easy, me? Arranging
your funeral? Talking the kids round?

07:59.840 --> 08:02.991
Telling them Daddy loved them,
but he's safe in the arms of Allah

08:03.080 --> 08:04.957
and one day
we're all going to be reunited?

08:05.040 --> 08:07.110
Not realising it were gonna be
so fucking soon.

08:07.200 --> 08:08.189
I made a mistake!

08:08.280 --> 08:10.874
You made more than one, Kash.

08:10.960 --> 08:14.111
- Get out.
- I've thought about you every day.

08:15.240 --> 08:16.434
I've missed you.

08:16.520 --> 08:21.435
Look, it wasn't until I lost you
that I realised how much I wanted you.

08:22.400 --> 08:25.153
I can tell them I had an accident.
A breakdown.

08:25.240 --> 08:27.800
I lost my memory,
didn't know who I was.

08:27.880 --> 08:31.111
Hang on. What are you talking about?

08:31.200 --> 08:33.998
I want to be a father to our children.

08:35.760 --> 08:37.159
Husband to me wife.

08:38.840 --> 08:41.400
Take me back.

09:04.040 --> 09:06.349
H20, 100%.

09:15.920 --> 09:19.230
It's only one night, Dad. Just keep
thinking about Liam and Stella.

09:19.320 --> 09:21.754
We need them back home
where they belong. With us.

09:21.840 --> 09:24.070
The place isn't the same
without them.

09:24.160 --> 09:26.151
I'm glad I've not had a drink.

09:26.240 --> 09:27.912
I'm glad I'm clear-headed.

09:28.000 --> 09:29.592
- Yeah?
- Mmm.

09:30.840 --> 09:34.310
Might never have noticed what
a fine young man you've turned into.

09:39.120 --> 09:40.394
FRANK FARTS

09:42.360 --> 09:46.512
- What's that?
- Biriyani. What can I say?

09:54.440 --> 09:55.668
MUSIC STOPS

10:06.360 --> 10:07.429
Give us a minute.

10:09.440 --> 10:10.475
Move!

10:20.400 --> 10:21.913
Thanks for dropping the charges.

10:24.120 --> 10:26.918
Hang on. You did me a favour.

10:27.000 --> 10:29.639
You didn't give me one of
your fucking kidneys.

10:29.720 --> 10:33.315
Sorry. I always smile
when I'm nervous.

10:33.400 --> 10:36.153
I know what I did,
and I know it was wrong.

10:36.240 --> 10:38.834
But I give you my word,
it'll never happen again.

10:38.920 --> 10:40.273
I know.

10:40.360 --> 10:43.511
I love her. I can't imagine me
living without your daughter.

10:43.600 --> 10:46.637
- You're right there.
- I'll do whatever it takes.

10:58.680 --> 10:59.874
Drink?

11:05.000 --> 11:08.629
Whoa, spread 'em, Frank.
It's a drug-free zone from now on.

11:08.720 --> 11:11.075
All usual suspects to be frisked
at regular intervals.

11:11.160 --> 11:12.149
I'm going home!

11:12.240 --> 11:14.879
0h, can we just get on with it,
please?

11:14.960 --> 11:17.633
I don't want to touch you any more
than you want to be touched, OK?

11:17.720 --> 11:19.915
This is an infringement
of me human rights.

11:20.000 --> 11:22.594
That'd be true,
if you were half fucking human.

11:24.640 --> 11:27.632
It's prescription.
It's for when I get me bad heads.

11:27.720 --> 11:29.392
- Like now?
- No...

11:29.480 --> 11:30.356
Ohh!

11:30.440 --> 11:32.954
Consider that your
final warning, Frank.

11:34.600 --> 11:37.592
- Oh, I don't believe it!
- Pissed already?

11:37.680 --> 11:40.956
I'm not under the influence of anything.
How many more fucking times?

11:41.040 --> 11:43.554
For God's sake, Frank.

12:01.000 --> 12:04.151
- You wouldn't be money laundering?
- That's exactly what I'm doing.

12:05.400 --> 12:07.834
And 10% of it's ours.

12:11.120 --> 12:11.916
Since when?

12:12.000 --> 12:15.390
Since I renegotiated
my terms and conditions.

12:16.320 --> 12:20.598
And once we've got enough, we can
retire from the family business and...

12:20.680 --> 12:21.749
And what?

12:25.080 --> 12:27.435
Mum being inside,

12:27.520 --> 12:31.832
Dad going through, well,
what he's been through...

12:31.920 --> 12:35.196
kind of got me thinking
what I want from life.

12:35.280 --> 12:37.874
What's important to me and who.

12:37.960 --> 12:41.839
You know your family's important
to you. We've always known that.

12:41.920 --> 12:44.309
You know how hard
I've had to work to get that together?

12:44.400 --> 12:47.517
How many heads I've had to crack?
The risks I've taken?

12:47.600 --> 12:50.672
And I know Mam and Dad said
I could have a bigger piece of the pie,

12:50.760 --> 12:54.389
but I'm wondering...
why can't I have a pie of me own?

12:58.680 --> 13:00.352
Yes, lads?

