14:02.920 --> 14:06.071
- Where?
- Home. Got to stay clean, haven't I?

14:06.160 --> 14:10.039
Sober. And like the three wise monkeys
keep on fucking saying,

14:10.120 --> 14:13.351
it's just one night.

14:24.320 --> 14:27.437
If you're doing this for me, then don't.

14:27.520 --> 14:30.990
