have been facing life for murder

15:02.040 --> 15:03.473
if that twat hadn't survived.

15:03.560 --> 15:07.838
All I'm saying is, I want more
for the effort I'm putting in.

15:07.920 --> 15:10.798
For you and me, for our future.

15:10.880 --> 15:13.155
I'm tired of carrying passengers, Karen.

15:13.240 --> 15:15.276
