15:15.360 --> 15:19.319
Mam says put it on slate.
See you later.

15:19.400 --> 15:22.790
Er, no, you won't. Karen and I
are having an early night.

15:22.880 --> 15:25.348
It's me mam's welcome home do!
You've got to be there.

15:25.440 --> 15:27.556
I don't got to be anywhere.

15:27.640 --> 15:29.995
Look, tell her I'll see her tomorrow.

15:33.720 --> 15:35.950
I'm not just a Maguire.

15:36.040 --> 15:39.077
I'm Jamie Maguire.
You're Karen Maguire.

15:40.680 --> 15:43.513
This... is my family.

15:46.280 --> 15:47.235
OK.

15:48.480 --> 15:52.155
Now, your arm here...
and my arm there.

15:52.240 --> 15:55.152
Now, take the weight on the balls...

