we - faked the whole thing?

16:42.800 --> 16:45.997
- They'll come round!
- Kash, please!

16:46.080 --> 16:47.559
I'm begging you.

16:47.640 --> 16:50.757
Have anything you want.
Just leave the kids out of it, please.

16:50.840 --> 16:53.274
I love you.

16:54.560 --> 16:56.437
I don't love you.

16:56.520 --> 17:00.433
And you coming back here
could fuck up everything I've got.

17:00.520 --> 17:02.397
The kids, Stan...

17:02.480 --> 17:04.277
Stan Waterman?

17:04.359 --> 17:06.351
He's the best thing
that's ever happened to me.

17:06.440 --> 17:08.556
I've got no chance, have I?

17:10.760 --> 17:13.797
Three years too late. I'm sorry.

17:13.880 --> 17:16.234
I've moved on. We all have.

17:16.319 --> 17:18.117
So should you.

17:18.200 --> 17:22.512
Start a new life. Get married again,
if that's what you need to do.

17:22.599 --> 17:24.511
How am I supposed to do that?

17:24.599 --> 17:28.148
- I haven't got a penny to my name.
- I can help.

17:28.240 --> 17:31.312
