by now, eh?

17:41.160 --> 17:42.388
Good night last night.

17:44.440 --> 17:46.158
Have to keep our eye on Joe.

17:46.240 --> 17:49.630
I think Joe knows if he ever laid
a hand on a child of ours again

17:49.720 --> 17:51.790
