out of what's mine...

18:15.960 --> 18:17.678
Here you go, with "me" and "mine".

18:17.760 --> 18:21.230
- I own 50% of everything we've got.
- I'm not arguing with that.

18:21.320 --> 18:26.110
All's I'm saying is, from now on,
there's one boss.

18:26.200 --> 18:27.394
Me.

18:28.480 --> 18:32.109
<i>We built this business. Me and you.</i>

18:32.200 --> 18:35.431
And if you think I'm going to
turn into some little Hausfrau

18:35.520 --> 18:40.992
just so you can shag your way
through your mid-life crisis...

18:41.080 --> 18:42.593
think again.

